skins.shipDescription: First ship of the Ise-class battleships, Ise.
skins.selfIntroduction: Ise, first ship of the Ise-class battleships! I was on perimeter guard when Pearl Harbor was attacked. I was then recalled and remodeled as an aviation battleship. Then I was recalled again... Tsk! Some ships have a long list of battles, but no one was patient enough to wait for me to join in! We're super dreadnought ships... You would think they'd want our help! *Sigh* Anyways, it's great to finally catch up with the main fleet!
skins.acquisition: I'm the Sakura Empire battleship who fired the last full volley during the war: Ise-Class battleship, Ise!
skins.login: Let's go have a swell time on the seas, Commander!
skins.details: Commander, allow me to show you what real bullet hell looks like!
skins.secretaryIdle1: We're fine without fuel. All you need out on the seas is some good food and booze!
skins.secretaryIdle2: What should I call Fusou? Big sister? Senpai?
skins.secretaryIdle3: Ise Shrine? I've seen it from a distance, but they won't let me go in...
skins.secretaryTouch: What? W-What do you mean an aviation battleship can't fly? Lame!
skins.secretarySpecialTouch: Commander, you really want to know what it feels like to fly, don't you? Please feel free to climb into my cannon.

skins.shipDescription: Planes: check! Main guns: check! Nobody can stop me now! Let's sortie right now, Commander! I'm fired up and wanna wreak some havoc on the battlefield!
skins.acquisition: Planes: check! Main guns: check! Nobody can stop me now! Let's sortie right now, Commander! I'm fired up and wanna wreak some havoc on the battlefield!
skins.login: Commander, my guns are gonna rust up if you keep me in port forever.
skins.secretaryIdle1: Damn... Guess aviation battleships can't fly, after all. Kinda let down, honestly...
skins.secretaryIdle2: What? I can't let my aircraft fly around the port whenever I want? Why not?!
skins.secretaryIdle3: Phew... What a nice day! Maybe I'll call over Hyuuga later so we can all go for some drinks. Whaddya say, Commander?
skins.secretaryTouch: You interested in my flight deck?
skins.secretarySpecialTouch: Aviation battleships can't fly, but if you want me to send you flying, then I'll grant your wish.
